    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">
            <!-- "Discover Delicious,Effortless Recipes,Extraordinary Flavors â€“ Your Journey to Simply Amazing Meals Starts Here!" -->
            Huge selection of Delicious, Effortless Recipes and Extraordinary Flavors.
        </h1>
